{"tid":1780102,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"何君堯登Google香港年度熱搜“熱爆本地話題人物”榜首","createTime":"2019-12-12T06:24:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T06:27:41.000Z","uid":9861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c844aad7e37ab27f1617f814ed813c22e86abf0a","tid":1780102,"uid":9861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T06:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DaF24pu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDaF24pu.jpg&h=049d5147&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港中通社12月11日電 搜索網站Google於11日公布2019年香港熱門搜索排行榜，反映過去一年香港人最關心的本地和國際時事熱話、風雲人物，以及流行文化等。今年的榜首都與香港的時事政局息息相關。其中立法會議員何君堯成為&ldquo;熱爆本地話題人物&rdquo;榜首位。<br />\n<br />\n  據香港媒體報道，今年&ldquo;熱爆本地話題人物&rdquo;榜的上榜人物幾乎全部與香港社會風波有關，除了榜首的何君堯，排次位的是特首林鄭月娥，其他還有香港警務處處長鄧炳強、主持警方記者會的謝振中、香港電臺記者利君雅，以及引發社會風波的陳同佳。<br />\n<br />\n  網上平臺&ldquo;連登&rdquo;居&ldquo;熱爆關鍵字&rdquo;及&ldquo;熱爆本地頭條&rdquo;兩個排行榜榜首。&ldquo;連儂墻&rdquo;成為香港年度&ldquo;最熱爆的意思搜尋&rdquo;，而李小龍的經典名言&ldquo;Be water&rdquo;和李嘉誠就社會議題於報章刊登廣告的&ldquo;黃臺之瓜，何堪再摘&rdquo;亦同時上榜。"},{"pid":"29f8e2b0792deca7f996cc6c871f5a2b0377686c","tid":1780102,"uid":294221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T06:26:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/27Y0Qxo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F27Y0Qxo.jpg&h=f8d2ca9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人嘅最強後盾</span></span><br />\n<br />\n專攻BNO平權<br />\n幫手解答BNO問題<br />\n<br />\n#MagnitskyAct #BNOisBritish #WeAreBritish #RightTheWrong #SaveBritish #SOSHK<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nJoin us: <a href=\"https://t.me/addoiluk1023\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Faddoiluk1023&d=Vh0AUGqI%2BhuKY3uG7C8Fcxfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=a37073ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/addoiluk1023</a>"},{"pid":"c0e650f42a3768b7d951a94d13030e591da19844","tid":1780102,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T06:27:41.000Z","msg":"咩年代 仲用「熱爆」<br />\n好撚老尷"}]}